ETrun client files
==================

Compatibility
-------------

Supported OS (32-bit & 64-bit):

* Windows 7 and newer
* Linux
* MacOS

Check https://github.com/ETrun/ETrun/blob/master/README.md for more information.

Installing
----------

Put ETrun-XXX.pk3 in etrun/ folder.

Refer to https://github.com/ETrun/ETrun/wiki/ETrun-cvars to configure your settings.
